ince the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Peder Pedersen Vendelbo was born about 1280, in Viborg, Denmark as the son of Peder Saxesen Vendelbo and Sophie Andersdatter. He married Sofie Andersdatter Hvide about 1316, in Denmark. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died on 12 April 1346, in Denmark, at the age of 67."},"et":{"about 1280–12 April 1346":"umbes 1280–12. aprill 1346","1280–1346":"1280–1346","1320–1400":"1320–1400","–Female":"Surnud","1292–1380":"1292–1380","1319–1359":"1319–1359","–Male":"Surnud","12 April 1346":"12. aprill 1346","1359":"1359","about 1280":"umbes 1280","about 1319":"umbes 1319","1346":"1346","about 1316":"umbes 1316","1400":"1400","1320":"1320","1319":"1319","1380":"1380","1292":"1292","1280":"1280","Denmark":"Taani","Viborg, Denmark":"Viborg, Taani"},"fi":{"about 1280–12 April 1346":"noin 1280–12. huhtikuuta 1346","1280–1346":"1280–1346","1320–1400":"1320–1400","–Female":"Kuollut","1292–1380":"1292–1380","1319–1359":"1319–1359","–Male":"Kuollut","12 April 1346":"12. huhtikuuta 1346","1359":"1359","about 1280":"noin 1280","about 1319":"noin 1319","1346":"1346","about 1316":"noin 1316","1400":"1400","1320":"1320","1319":"1319","1380":"1380","1292":"1292","1280":"1280","Denmark":"Tanska","Viborg, Denmark":"Viborg, Tanska"},"fr":{"about 1280–12 April 1346":"environ 1280–12 avril 1346","1280–1346":"1280–1346","1320–1400":"1320–1400","–Female":"Décédée","1292–1380":"1292–1380","1319–1359":"1319–1359","–Male":"Décédé","12 April 1346":"12 avril 1346","1359":"1359","about 1280":"environ 1280","about 1319":"environ 1319","1346":"1346","about 1316":"environ 1316","1400":"1400","1320":"1320","1319":"1319","1380":"1380","1292":"1292","1280":"1280","Denmark":"Danemark","Viborg, Denmark":"Viborg, Danemark","lifeSummary":"Peder Pedersen Vendelbo est né environ 1280, à Viborg, Danemark, fils de Peder Saxesen Vendelbo et Sophie Andersdatter. Il a épousé Sofie Andersdatter Hvide environ 1316, à Danemark. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Il est dé